article.headline: Louisiana Tech 92, Tougaloo 58
article.story: RUSTON, La. (AP) -- Paul Millsap scored 25 points and grabbed eight rebounds as Louisiana Tech took a 92-58 victory over Tougaloo on Thursday night. Corey Dean scored 11 for Tech (7-5), which led 45-21 by halftime and was never threatened. Tech got 15 players into the game and 12 of them scored. Brandon Caston led all scorers with 29 points for Tougaloo (2-8). Marvin McDonald added 19 points, but Tougaloo got little scoring from anyone else and finished the game with a 30.8 shooting percentage from the field. Louisiana Tech shot 43.2 percent and outscored Tougaloo 22-9 from the foul line. <
